name: Sensapp
body:
### Welcome to SensApp Setup Pages.

To install SensApp on your computer, just execute the following steps: 

```
$ git://github.com/mosser/SensApp.git
$ cd SensApp/
$ cd net.modelbased.sensapp
$ mvn clean install
```
